            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName key="#Freeborn"><name ref="Liutbertus"
                            >Liutpert</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Freeborn">homo liber</rs> et filio quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Teudericus">Teuderici</name></persName>, quia per cartula ad
                        resedendo confirmasti me et filiis et nepotibus meis tu venerabili domno
                            <persName ref="#people/343">Peredeo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopo</rs> in <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            >casa</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Mother_churches"><rs
                                key="#Mother_churches">ecclesie</rs> vestre</orgName> in loco
                            <placeName key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions"
                            >Ligori</placeName>, ubi antea ressidet quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Ursulus">Ursulo</name></persName>, et in omnes <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">res</rs> ividem pertenentes. <foreign>Perciò
                            promette per sé, i figli e i nipoti</foreign> ut diebus vite nostre in
                        ipsa casa abitare debeamus et ipsa casa et honnes res ividem pertenentes in
                        omnibus meliorare debeamus et in alio loco aut in alia casa peculiarina
                        facere non debeamus. Et per singulo anno (…) reddere debeamus de ipsa res
                            <rs key="#Rent_in_kind">duo modia <rs key="#Maiores">grano</rs> et duo
                            modia <rs key="#Minores">farre</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vino</rs> anforas
                            quinque, <rs key="#Oil">olivas</rs> medietate, <rs key="#Animals"
                                >animale</rs> bono magese, in Pascha pario uno <rs key="#Poultry"
                                >pullos</rs>, ovas decen</rs>, et <rs key="#Operae">angaria</rs>
                        vobis facere debeamus, sicut est consuetudo vobis facere alii massarii de
                        ipso loco. <foreign>Pena</foreign>: auri solidos trigenta. (…) Actum
                            <placeName ref="#places/4">Luca</placeName>.
                            <foreign>Sottoscrizioni</foreign>: + Liutpert promissori; (ss) <persName
                            key="#Witness #Subdeacons"><name ref="Gausprandus"
                            >Gausprandus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Subdeacons">subdiaconus</rs>; + <persName
                            key="#Witness #Other_clerics"><name ref="Pertipertus"
                            >Pertiperti</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clerici</rs> testis; + <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Fratellus de Trasusare">Fratelli</name></persName> filio
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Gumbertus">Gunperti</name></persName> de
                            <placeName>Trasusare</placeName> testis. <foreign>Scrive</foreign>:
                            <persName key="#Writer #Deacons"><name ref="Osprandus"
                            >Osprandus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diaconus</rs>.</ab>
                        </div>
